Description:
This is a sanity check that Kade can fire off to ensure that all main parts of Kollective IQ are working.  Basic functionality that Kade can report is working, with no unexpected results:
-Login/Logout
-Navigation interactions
-Main dashboard data (Summary pages)

Description: This will cover primarily the log in process and validation of Sudoing as a different user
Fires up the browser
Filling out login info (username)
Filling out login info (password)
Clicks the Stay Logged In button
Clicks the Submit button to login
Waits for all angular elements to load and throws an exception if it take longer than 60 seconds.
